    • Method Detail

      • isCataphoric

        public static boolean isCataphoric​(ExpressionType type,
                                   SurfaceElement su)
        Determines whether a mention is cataphoric. A mention is considered cataphoric if it is nominal AND (it contains the token following OR it is the first textual unit of the document).
        Parameters:
        type - the expression type to consider
        su - the textual unit in question
        Returns:
        true if the mention is cataphoric

        Returns:
        a set of semantic objects that are coreferential mentions associated with the textual unit
